Package: quickclocks
Type: Package
Title: Unified Epigenetic Clock Calculator
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2025-01-09
Authors@R: person("Brian", "Chen", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "brian.chen4@ucsf.edu")
Description: Calculate 40+ epigenetic clocks from DNA methylation data with a
    single function call. Integrates SeSAMe (IDAT preprocessing), EpiDISH
    (cell type deconvolution via RPC and CP methods), DunedinPACE, PC-Clocks,
    epiTOC2, and methylCIPHER. Supports EPICv2, EPIC, 450K, 27K, and MSA arrays.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/brianchengithub/quickclocks
BugReports: https://github.com/brianchengithub/quickclocks/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
